  <brief_title>ZIMURA in Combination With Eylea in Patients With Idiopathic Polypoidal Choroidal Vasculopathy (IPCV)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2A Open-Label Trial to Assess the Safety of ZIMURA™ (Anti-C5) in Combination With EYLEA® in Treatment Experienced Subjects With Idiopathic Polypoidal Choroidal Vasculopathy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
