  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To asses the safety of intravitreal Zimura™ (complement factor C5 inhibitor) administered in
      combination with Eylea® in treatment experienced subjects with idiopathic polypoidal
      choroidal vasculopathy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
